{"tid":306520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(圖)幪面超人有咩得罪你班香港人","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T16:09:08.000Z","uid":54728,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65a4bdc81f184e186968ad1ba7f1461eb6c7d911","tid":306520,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:06:59.000Z","msg":"人睇韓劇，有人睇，有人追捧，就叫正常<br />\n屌你老母睇幪面超人就俾人話低b，on9，弱智，我話你聽無睇過幪面超人先係真正唔正常個批。<br />\n仲有就算只係睇過一兩集，一兩部的人就唔好話自己幪面超人迷，成日只係識攞而家同以前比，根本衝出黎柒，每一部都有佢自己特色，劇情又唔睇，只在乎變身特效靚唔靚，膠唔膠，你不如對住d韓狗打飛機算啦，都係睇樣姐有咩唔同？<br />\n而家仲要俾d垃圾fb page 當講玩笑，我真係睇唔過眼<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/02/230427_2fbb24316dc67caab6b10ae4a9ecb879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F02%2F230427_2fbb24316dc67caab6b10ae4a9ecb879.jpg&h=568abf98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抱歉講野1999，但真係好嬲"},{"pid":"be095381a9974db470383d0a044d06658c54fb94","tid":306520,"uid":44211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"uwants係咁，呢期成日拎返d拉打同動畫嚟鞭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b931b1606faf340121806dae96b8e0388e624f4","tid":306520,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:11:24.000Z","msg":"今次開post只係想令大家對任何事都公平對待，唔好咩都唔知就胡亂定奪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32971634538e75259943d561ed83cc36abb5b714","tid":306520,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:11:40.000Z","msg":"ex-aid劇情好過大部分韓劇"},{"pid":"c2b562619f35a39b928f3f5bc699b6f691e26402","tid":306520,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>uwants係咁，呢期成日拎返d拉打同動畫嚟鞭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇到其他post都係不斷數其他動漫，都唔明點解仲會有人like"},{"pid":"31c7b64c81ebefaa7ad5374909f0ceff1012bebd","tid":306520,"uid":17110,"like":0,"dislike":0,